<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Verification Update</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background: #EF4444; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
        .content { background: #f9f9f9; padding: 30px; }
        .button { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 30px; background: #4F46E5; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; }
        .footer { text-align: center; padding: 20px; color: #666; font-size: 12px; }
        .rejection-box { background: #FEF2F2; border: 1px solid #FECACA; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 8px; }
        .help-box { background: #EFF6FF; border: 1px solid #DBEAFE; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 8px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Verification Update</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Hi {{name}},</h2>
            <p>We've reviewed your student verification request, but unfortunately, we couldn't approve it at this time.</p>

            <div class="rejection-box">
                <h3>Reason for Rejection:</h3>
                <p><strong>{{rejectionReason}}</strong></p>
                {{#if additionalNotes}}
                <p><em>Additional Notes: {{additionalNotes}}</em></p>
                {{/if}}
            </div>

            <h3>What You Can Do:</h3>

            <div class="help-box">
                <h4>üìù Re-submit Your Verification</h4>
                <p>You can re-submit your verification with corrected documents. Please address the issues mentioned above and try again.</p>
                <a href="{{resubmitUrl}}" class="button">Re-submit Verification</a>
            </div>

            <h3>Common Issues and Solutions:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Unclear Documents:</strong> Upload high-quality, well-lit photos</li>
                <li><strong>Name Mismatch:</strong> Ensure the name matches your registered account</li>
                <li><strong>Expired ID:</strong> Use a current, valid student ID</li>
                <li><strong>Missing Information:</strong> Complete all required fields</li>
            </ul>

            <p><strong>Need Help?</strong></p>
            <p>If you believe this was a mistake or need assistance with your verification, our support team is here to help.</p>

            <a href="{{supportUrl}}" class="button">Contact Support</a>

            <hr style="margin: 30px 0; border: none; border-top: 1px solid #ddd;">
            <p style="color: #666; font-size: 14px;">
                You can re-submit verification requests after 24 hours.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2024 TalabaHub. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>University Students Platform for Uzbekistan</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>